{"tid":905674,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)盜海豪情3 舊版蝙蝠俠 殺出個黎明","createTime":"2018-11-17T10:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T16:35:15.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"60141a310b3c9d641a4bc546b707111ff496f1df","tid":905674,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c9448089\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5f7bcd10\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3240d68d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.movierulz.to/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/The-Invasion-2007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.movierulz.to%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F04%2FThe-Invasion-2007.jpg&h=56d3683f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/644223/org/717d3311a48989cac099b9ca8422b18a.jpg/ipOoTUa1MO2XyFpG4ZN1fGe9F7-XSRAsgyKfiYMin4k?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F644223%2Forg%2F717d3311a48989cac099b9ca8422b18a.jpg%2FipOoTUa1MO2XyFpG4ZN1fGe9F7-XSRAsgyKfiYMin4k%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=bb8d5668&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.ihd.me/poster/lpst/p759442350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ihd.me%2Fposter%2Flpst%2Fp759442350.jpg&h=71b40fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.魯本&middot;迪什科夫（艾略特&middot;高德飾）患心肌梗塞後，丹尼爾&middot;奧申（喬治&middot;克隆尼飾）等十人圍在他的病床前。四星期前，拉斯維加斯賭場大亨威利&middot;班克（艾爾&middot;帕西諾飾）與魯本在二人合資的新賭場工地中見面。魯本為班克爭取到了關鍵的合同後，班克使出老手段，迫使他交出股份。過度的驚嚇使魯本犯了心臟病。<br />\n奧申等人發誓要為魯本復仇，要在班克的酒店正式開業當晚使其破產。為了達到這個目標，所有的賭客都必須贏錢。由於資金不足，班克在新酒店的建設過程中不得不向一些競爭對手尋求幫助，並將他們安排在了董事會中。如果酒店在第一季度中不能獲利五億美元，班克就會失去他的董事長席位.....<br />\n<br />\n2.在高譚城，蝙蝠俠阻止了由雙面人引起的一起銀行人質事件，但雙面人還是逃脫了，他以前曾是地區檢察官哈維&middot;登特，因為遭受了巨大的不幸而變成一個邪惡的魔頭。愛德華&middot;奈格瑪是韋恩企業的一名研究人員，他開發出一種可以直接和人腦相連接的機器，通曉他人思想並加以控制的機器。布魯斯&middot;韋恩認為這樣的發明會引起太多的爭議，因此拒絕採納。愛德華於是憤怒地殺死了自己的上司並偽造成自殺後辭職<br />\n<br />\n3.神出鬼沒的蝙蝠俠，這回將面臨此生中最強勁的對手&mdash;急凍人、毒藤女和他的跟班&mdash;班恩。勇敢機敏的蝙蝠女孩與蝙蝠俠和羅賓聯手，同與邪惡的罪犯展開了對戰..<br />\n<br />\n4.《殺出個黎明》是羅伯特&middot;羅德里格茲執導，喬治&middot;克魯尼、昆汀&middot;塔倫蒂諾等主演的電影。在弟弟理查德&middot;傑科的幫助下，大盜塞思&middot;傑科越獄成功。兩人在逃亡的路上殺死多名警探。他們只有逃到墨西哥境內才有生路。在一家汽車旅館裡，傑科兄弟劫持了牧師雅各布&middot;富勒和他的兩個孩子。在他們的掩護下，傑科兄弟躲過了警方的搜查，順利地到達了墨西哥境內..<br />\n<br />\n6 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=2c95cd85\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9aacb738\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ed09420c63df0c81e14b6ba2f178a62f2c9149","tid":905674,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vinnieh.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/oceans-thirteen-cast.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvinnieh.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F12%2Foceans-thirteen-cast.jpg&h=4b4328f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8f67d076543348049a427835f6de14697026a61","tid":905674,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef2983cd594ed5e866e1bdf9cd60dcbd6ab9ea0","tid":905674,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f482a83a0ac61edb38678ca2de56ecd291641e1","tid":905674,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c31b97c994d99d43792252904803ba59a008110","tid":905674,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab28b105acc28bc8ba55d29c195d69576a92d39b","tid":905674,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislik